the code is divided into the server and yhe client programs ,

steps to run : 

compile the server code with 
gcc -o client client.c 
start the sevrve using the command ./server <textfilename>

compile the client in seperate window
gcc -0 client client.c
there is a bash script that runs xtern windows along with the client and the usage is 
./spawn_clients.sh <no. of clients>

all the scripts must be run in the bash environment